TableContextTimeStampAfterTable: {16263=     HEAP - Help with Heating Bills                              Need some help with those winter heating bills?  On Monday, February 6th from 9:00 a.m. to 1:00 p.m. Bambi Cameron, from Ohio District 5 Area Agency on Aging will be here to answer questions and help you fill out an application.  You will need proof of citizenship (birth certificate or voter registration card) along with a current heating and electric bill, and proof of income.  Bambi will be seated in front of fireplace.  Call 387-6100 if you have any questions.  }
